that CIA document,

00:54:12.980 --> 00:54:15.900 align:middle line:10%
he expressed his
heartfelt feelings,

00:54:15.900 --> 00:54:20.470 align:middle line:10%
his respect for Marilyn
and his sense of sorrow

00:54:20.470 --> 00:54:22.130 align:middle line:10%
over all of this.

00:54:22.130 --> 00:54:24.840 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Let's go to
that film clip now.

00:54:24.840 --> 00:54:26.650 align:middle line:84%
>>Marilyn was an
extraordinary person.

00:54:26.650 --> 00:54:32.070 align:middle line:10%
She was so different from
the Hollywood construct

00:54:32.070 --> 00:54:33.820 align:middle line:10%
that it's almost
not recognizable.

00:54:33.820 --> 00:54:36.410 align:middle line:90%
She was intelligent.

00:54:36.410 --> 00:54:37.870 align:middle line:90%
She was well read.

00:54:37.870 --> 00:54:40.370 align:middle line:84%
She loved the music
of Bela Bartok.

00:54:40.370 --> 00:54:42.830 align:middle line:90%
I mean, she read Thomas Hardy.

00:54:42.830 --> 00:54:44.140 align:middle line:90%
She read James Joyce.

00:54:44.140 --> 00:54:45.470 align:middle line:90%
She read Shakespeare.

00:54:45.470 --> 00:54:47.510 align:middle line:84%
We can't bring her
back, but we can

00:54:47.510 --> 00:54:49.710 align:middle line:84%
remedy some of what's
been done to her memory.

00:54:49.710 --> 00:54:53.820 align:middle line:84%
It's a national disgrace
what was done to her.

00:54:53.820 --> 00:54:56.070 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Again, thank you
so much for taking the time

00:54:56.070 --> 00:54:58.610 align:middle line:84%
to do such a fabulous
job on this documentary.

00:54:58.610 --> 00:55:01.775 align:middle line:84%
It was very enlightening and
about people that, you know,

00:55:01.775 --> 00:55:04.500 align:middle line:84%
it's still our Camelot in
our own hearts and minds

00:55:04.500 --> 00:55:06.920 align:middle line:84%
about the beauty that each
of these people exemplified,

00:55:06.920 --> 00:55:11.370 align:middle line:84%
regardless of the dark side of
human nature at times as well.

00:55:11.370 --> 00:55:13.690 align:middle line:84%
So I want to thank you for
doing that for us and all

00:55:13.690 --> 00:55:15.177 align:middle line:90%
